  "body": "When this RPC method is called for \"pending\" block, we should be querying the transaction pool for the latest nonce of a transaction sent from the specified account. Currently this is not supported. This will require some modifications in here: https://github.com/ledgerwatch/interfaces/blob/b9b02cb6a62f8b7e2bb689b148492d0e4ad6d836/txpool/txpool.proto#L55 to add a function for querying latest nonce of a specific account",
